1
00:00:19,162 --> 00:00:24,349
ظآزThe whole world is lit upظآز

2
00:00:24,350 --> 00:00:25,661
ظآزBecause you existظآز

3
00:00:25,662 --> 00:00:27,741
ظآزYou're alwaysظآز

4
00:00:27,742 --> 00:00:32,391
ظآزSomewhere close, flying with meظآز

5
00:00:32,392 --> 00:00:35,124
ظآزGo to where the wind blowsظآز

6
00:00:35,125 --> 00:00:36,691
ظآزHold tightظآز

7
00:00:36,692 --> 00:00:42,481
ظآزTo the ray of light that belongs to usظآز

8
00:00:42,482 --> 00:00:47,932
=Wild & Fiery=
=Episode 13=

9
00:00:48,259 --> 00:00:49,019
Ms. Mu,

10
00:00:49,379 --> 00:00:50,820
Mr. Mu specifically instructed

11
00:00:51,019 --> 00:00:52,618
that you must fulfill his last wish.

12
00:00:52,619 --> 00:00:53,338
Only then

13
00:00:53,339 --> 00:00:54,860
will you be able to inherit the estate.

14
00:00:58,112 --> 00:01:00,961
(Last Will)

15
00:01:00,962 --> 00:01:02,640
(Marry and have a child
whose surname follows the mother's.)

16
00:01:02,640 --> 00:01:05,620
(Only after fulfilling this condition will
the other inheritance terms take effect.)

17
00:01:09,020 --> 00:01:10,138
(Marriage?)

18
00:01:10,139 --> 00:01:12,739
(Have a child
whose surname follows the mother's?)

19
00:01:12,859 --> 00:01:13,780
Zhiyu,

20
00:01:14,940 --> 00:01:18,140
what did your dad write in the will?

21
00:01:18,859 --> 00:01:21,260
That's none of your business.
You don't need to know.

22
00:01:31,380 --> 00:01:32,498
My heart breaks

23
00:01:32,499 --> 00:01:34,140
seeing Zhiyu like this.

24
00:01:34,979 --> 00:01:37,819
She probably still can't accept
her dad's death.

25
00:01:39,380 --> 00:01:41,659
Since Zhiyu isn't in the right mood
to tell me.

26
00:01:42,219 --> 00:01:43,459
How about

27
00:01:43,979 --> 00:01:45,260
you tell me instead, Mr. Wang?

28
00:01:46,419 --> 00:01:47,338
This might

29
00:01:47,339 --> 00:01:49,138
involve Ms. Mu's privacy.

30
00:01:49,139 --> 00:01:50,299
If it's to be made public,

31
00:01:50,300 --> 00:01:52,218
we should first get her permission.

32
00:01:52,219 --> 00:01:54,179
As his wife,

33
00:01:54,180 --> 00:01:55,338
am I not qualified

34
00:01:55,339 --> 00:01:57,099
to know my husband's will?

35
00:01:58,460 --> 00:01:59,340
Uh...

36
00:01:59,380 --> 00:02:00,459
Mr. Wang,

37
00:02:00,460 --> 00:02:02,420
although Chenzhou has passed away,

38
00:02:02,619 --> 00:02:03,620
you can still

39
00:02:03,859 --> 00:02:06,379
continue working with the Mu Group.

40
00:02:11,659 --> 00:02:14,720
In the will, Mr. Mu required
that Ms. Mu must get married

41
00:02:14,720 --> 00:02:16,920
and promised that the child
she gives birth to will take her surname.

42
00:02:16,920 --> 00:02:19,180
Only then will she qualify
to inherit the estate.

43
00:02:19,339 --> 00:02:21,379
(So Yu has to get married?)

44
00:02:21,580 --> 00:02:23,818
(This old geezer really
went to great lengths)

45
00:02:23,819 --> 00:02:25,900
(to stop me from seizing
the family fortune.)

46
00:02:26,779 --> 00:02:29,299
(But as for Mu Zhiyu's future husband,)

47
00:02:29,300 --> 00:02:31,220
(I've already arranged that for her.)

48
00:02:35,099 --> 00:02:36,579
What did the will say

49
00:02:36,580 --> 00:02:37,939
to make you this uneasy?

50
00:02:40,900 --> 00:02:42,259
If I want to inherit the estate,

51
00:02:42,460 --> 00:02:43,780
I have to get married first.

52
00:02:44,219 --> 00:02:46,620
And if I have a child,
the child must take my mother's surname.

53
00:02:48,180 --> 00:02:49,539
(Marriage.)

54
00:02:49,700 --> 00:02:51,020
(Child takes the mother's surname.)

55
00:02:51,460 --> 00:02:53,699
(Chairman Mu was extremely meticulous.)

56
00:02:53,740 --> 00:02:55,979
(He set up protection against Xu Mingzhu
with this one will,)

57
00:02:55,980 --> 00:02:58,659
(prevented her from taking power directly,
protected his daughter,)

58
00:02:58,700 --> 00:03:01,099
(and ensured the family lineage
would continue.)

59
00:03:01,379 --> 00:03:02,340
(Impressive.)

60
00:03:04,860 --> 00:03:06,979
What I don't understand is

61
00:03:07,659 --> 00:03:08,979
that I'm his only daughter.

62
00:03:08,980 --> 00:03:11,659
Why do I have to get married first
before inheriting the estate?

63
00:03:22,619 --> 00:03:25,580
Maybe he hoped this would
bring you back to him.

64
00:03:26,180 --> 00:03:27,500
Or maybe

65
00:03:28,580 --> 00:03:30,340
it was meant to guard against
Xu Mingzhu,

66
00:03:33,260 --> 00:03:34,979
so you wouldn't be left alone
and helpless.

67
00:03:36,140 --> 00:03:37,419
Do you understand?

68
00:04:01,219 --> 00:04:03,220
Thank you, Shen Jibai.

69
00:04:05,059 --> 00:04:06,939
Thank you for being there for me.

70
00:04:10,460 --> 00:04:11,539
Shen Jibai!

71
00:04:13,779 --> 00:04:15,099
Don't touch Yu!

72
00:04:16,739 --> 00:04:17,579
Mr. He,

73
00:04:17,580 --> 00:04:18,659
