74
00:04:18,940 --> 00:04:20,379
This is a private area.

75
00:04:20,380 --> 00:04:21,499
You're just a bodyguard.

76
00:04:21,500 --> 00:04:23,658
How dare you lay your hands
on your employee? You...

77
00:04:23,659 --> 00:04:24,580
Enough.

78
00:04:25,659 --> 00:04:26,820
All of you, leave.

79
00:04:28,620 --> 00:04:30,059
I want to be alone for a while.

80
00:04:30,700 --> 00:04:31,739
Yu.

